import React from 'react'
import {ChakraProvider, Container, Box, Stack, Text} from '@chakra-ui/react'

const NewTweet = () => {
    const header_border = {
        borderBottom: "1px solid #38444D",
      };
    return (
        <ChakraProvider>
            <Box w="600px" h="120px" style={header_border} ml="-17px" bg="tomato">
                <Stack direction="column" ml="17px">
                    <Box>
                        <Stack direction="row" spacing="20px" mt="10px">
                            <Box w="50px" h="50px" bg="gray.50"></Box>
                            <Box>
                                <Text fontSize="19px" mt="10px">What's happening ?</Text>
                            </Box>
                        </Stack>
                    </Box>
                    <Box>
                        <Stack direction="row"  ml="70px" spacing="100px">
                            <Box>
                                <Stack direction="row" spacing="20px" mt="15px">
                                    <Box w="20px" h="20px" bg="gray.50"></Box>
                                    <Box w="20px" h="20px" bg="gray.50"></Box>
                                    <Box w="20px" h="20px" bg="gray.50"></Box>
                                    <Box w="20px" h="20px" bg="gray.50"></Box>
                                    <Box w="20px" h="20px" bg="gray.50"></Box>
                                </Stack>
                            </Box>
                            <Box w="75px" h="40px" bg="gray.50"></Box>
                        </Stack>
                    </Box>
                </Stack>
            </Box>
        </ChakraProvider>
    )
}

export default NewTweet
